PN,42901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778076676
OL,3,CBanned drug-driver jailed after 136mph
OL,4,Cpolice chase ends in fatal crash on A19
OL,6,FA banned driver high on drugs reached
OL,7,Fspeeds of 136mph while fleeing police
OL,8,Fbefore driving the wrong way down a
OL,9,Fdual carriageway and killing his
OL,10,Fgirlfriend in a head-on crash, a court
OL,11,Fhas heard.
OL,13,FKane Farragher, 24, was jailed for 12
OL,14,Fyears and nine months at Newcastle
OL,15,FCrown Court after admitting causing
OL,16,Fdeath by dangerous driving following
OL,17,Fthe crash that killed Taylor Jenkins
OL,18,Fon the A19 near Sunderland.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
