FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778076676
OL,3,CBanned drug-driver jailed after 136mph
OL,4,Cpolice chase ends in fatal crash on A19
OL,6,FThe court heard Farragher was
OL,7,Fdisqualified from driving and had
OL,8,Ftaken a cocktail of drugs including
OL,9,Fcocaine, cannabis, ecstasy and
OL,10,Fketamine, with some readings showing
OL,11,Fthat he was several times over the
OL,12,Flegal limits.
OL,14,FIn the early hours of 1 March,
OL,15,FFarragher's vehicle was flagged by
OL,16,FPolice Scotland as a "vehicle of
OL,17,Finterest", prompting Northumbria
OL,18,FPolice to assist in attempts to stop
OL,19,Fit and speak to the driver.
OL,26,@xD@VOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778076676
OL,3,CBanned drug-driver jailed after 136mph
OL,4,Cpolice chase ends in fatal crash on A19
OL,6,FThat intervention led to a police
OL,7,Fpursuit in Gateshead, before Farragher
OL,8,Fsped off, reaching speeds of up to
OL,9,F136mph.
OL,11,FOfficers later abandoned the chase
OL,12,Fafter he drove the wrong way onto the
OL,13,FA19.
OL,15,FMoments later, he collided head-on
OL,16,Fwith a taxi near the Nissan factory,
OL,17,Fkilling Ms Jenkins, who was in the
OL,18,Ffront passenger seat. A rear passenger
OL,19,Falso suffered skull and rib fractures.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778076676
OL,3,CBanned drug-driver jailed after 136mph
OL,4,Cpolice chase ends in fatal crash on A19
OL,6,FProsecutors said Farragher had only
OL,7,Frecently joined the A19 after a
OL,8,Fdangerous drive through Tyneside, with
OL,9,Fthe fatal impact occurring around
OL,10,Fseven miles from where the pursuit
OL,11,Fbegan.
OL,13,FThe court heard he was already banned
OL,14,Ffrom driving and had a previous
OL,15,Fconviction for dangerous driving
OL,16,Finvolving stolen motorbikes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
