FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778076676
OL,3,CBanned drug-driver jailed after 136mph
OL,4,Cpolice chase ends in fatal crash on A19
OL,6,FJudge Penny Moreland said he made a
OL,7,F"deliberate decision to ignore the
OL,8,Frules of the road" and showed
OL,9,F"complete disregard" for the danger to
OL,10,Fothers, describing the incident as a
OL,11,Fprolonged and highly dangerous course
OL,12,Fof driving.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@RO]qD@AOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
