OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,430,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1778076676
OL,3,CBanned drug-driver jailed after 136mph
OL,4,Cpolice chase ends in fatal crash on A19
OL,6,FVictim impact statements described Ms
OL,7,FJenkins, from Edinburgh, as a "loving,
OL,8,Fhard-working" young woman with her
OL,9,Flife ahead of her. Her father said her
OL,10,Floss was "beyond anything I can bear"
OL,11,F- and her sister Ellis Jenkins added
OL,12,Fthat "the impact of losing her is
OL,13,Fsomething I will carry with me
OL,14,Fforever."
OL,16,FAfter sentencing, police condemned
OL,17,FFarragher's actions, describing the
OL,18,Fdrugs in his system as "truly
OL,19,Fshocking" and saying he should never
OL,20,Fhave been behind the wheel.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@MO]rD@JOUvD@IO]zD@XOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
